And because all crisis is about the humans involved, we start there. WHAT SETS RAVENYARD APART Crisis management is typically handled by PR firms, but we believe that outward-facing communications are only one aspect of an incredibly complex picture. In a crisis, how do you communicate to your employees, your investors, your community? How do you balance your legal strategy and regulatory response with your brand reputation? And how do you manage the experience? Because crisis brings very specific challenges, our approach includes: OPERATIONAL RESPONSE TO CRISIS - Process-based orientation with checklists and timelines - Systematic communications analysis ​ SUPPORT FOR LEADERS AND TEAMS - Help to avoid burnout and distraction - Focus on how crisis affects family and community relationships ​ "WALK-IN-READY" TECHNICAL EXPERTISE - Deep experience in law, finance, and marketing/communications ​

Benefits: Accumi bases the equity split on data instead of gut feel guesses or negotiating skills. It is a fair way to split equity. And for bootstrapped startups that do not have a lot of cash, Accumi provides a mechanism to dish out equity in real time (like cash). This provides a great incentive system and enhances team engagement.

Description: Why Is It So Hard To Find A Doctor When You Need One? My name is Zinovi Kurolap. I am the CEO of MyDoctorCare.
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Why Is It So Hard To Find A Doctor When You Need One?    My name is Zinovi Kurolap. I am the CEO of MyDoctorCare Inc.     In May of 2014 I found out that I am one of millions of Americans with Type 2 diabetes I decided to take action and get treatment, but was frustrated at how difficult it was to find a doctor online!    With recent changes in healthcare, I realized that millions of people across the nation are struggling just like me, and I decided to do something to help fix the problem!     After months of planning, my team and I finally created MyDoctor.Care.     Our goal is to make it super quick and easy for anyone in the US to find the right doctor, anytime they need one, no matter where they live!  Best of all, our service is always free for patients, and all registered users are able to WIN all sorts of prizes at our periodic prize drawings just for using our website!    You may have heard that many doctors are really having a hard time adjusting to the times and finding new patients. In fact, recent surveys suggest that nearly half of active doctors are considering shutting down their practices within the next several years!     Can You Imagine How Much Of A Nightmare It Would Be To Find A Doctor If Half Of The Offices Open Today Were No Longer Operating In 5 Years?    We make it easy and affordable for doctors to attract more new patients, so they can spend their time and resources running their practice and helping those in need.. instead of worrying about marketing their business!    Unlike competing companies, we offer physicians a guaranteed placement at the top of our search results & a monthly flow of patients. We are launching dynamic digital and local marketing campaigns, including celebrity sponsorships and prize giveaways to help us accelerate our growth and attract thousands of patients across the US. We offer physicians a unique and cost-effective alternative to other services, which do not guarantee any results.
